ational solutions. This role will be responsible for recognizing and expressing value in all our social media tools, and for using those tools to the benefit of our customers.RESPONSIBILITIES:Explore and translate business requirements for customer marketing and technological platformsDevelop innovative marketing and technological platforms to demonstrate our value proposition and our software capabilitiesOnboard, debug and test large and complex systems that process millions of events in a batch and receive accurate time estimatesClearly articulate the strength and value proposition of our technologyFind solutions to difficult technical issues that our customers' stakeholders and customers cannot live without and develop tools to their workshopsHelp us execute marketing campaigns with superior, standards-compliant, and efficiency’d resultsBecome a strategic advisor - able to imagine the programs you would have developed yourself running a coding demo of your ideas through to production ready automated testingBe a leader in your field, or in a startup's ecosystem – you'll get to work with an established leader in one of the world’s most exciting and challenging verticalsAchieving line-ups of reps on day-to-day operations and management of time
